name: Morondanga Republik: The tremendous omnipresence of my cuántic hunger
description:
In the natural event of The Night of the Frogs* it is very common the presence of artists going in search of the effects of the vapors to get inspired or search for truths within their unconscious. 

From those explorations come works like this one, called "The tremendous omnipresence of my cuántic hunger" by an anonymous author. 

Large is the collection of lysergic-inspired works in the Morondanga Republik. Great is also the number of anonymous artists. Artists in this country tend to have very controlled egos. Perhaps this is another effect of the vapors.

*see OBJKT #245972
